{"tid":258263,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"杯子爆炸，京女門牙斷","createTime":"2017-05-26T03:02:52.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-26T03:15:55.000Z","uid":70946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5e9ad6aed41363a3b1662b4b0497e411e06f22d9","tid":258263,"uid":70946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T03:02:52.000Z","msg":"【看中國2017年5月25日訊】北京一名王姓女子，日前在家中使用玻璃杯喝水，結果玻璃杯突然發生爆炸，把該女子當場炸暈，門牙也被炸斷。<br />\n<br />\n大陸媒體報導，5月20日凌晨4時，北京市市民王姓女子想喝水，她起床走進廚房在玻璃杯中倒入常溫水準備飲用，豈料杯子剛舉到嘴邊就突然爆炸，把她當場炸暈。<br />\n<br />\n凌晨5時許，王女感到嘴角疼痛，照鏡子發現唇下有外傷，一顆門牙被炸掉。<br />\n<br />\n根據醫院診斷記錄，王女就醫時右下唇腫大，唇內有傷口，縫了4針，一顆門牙的牙冠折斷露髓，還有待後續治療。<br />\n<br />\n王女表示，爆炸玻璃杯是她1年前在北京宜家（IKEA）分店購入的水杯。<br />\n<br />\n對此，宜家北京市場部回應，若是產品品質問題造成消費者傷害或權益損失，宜家將承擔相應的賠償責任。目前，宜家正對產生問題的原因展開調查。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6219e8f287e18e0bd5ab2c338e4894c0c2f69e6","tid":258263,"uid":6329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T03:03:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a125c7396a30a50ea2f3d292f46a9e9bc500cb22","tid":258263,"uid":75893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T03:04:55.000Z","msg":"source?"},{"pid":"f04999cffea66aaee663769bfcb4808149f2d758","tid":258263,"uid":57911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T03:06:29.000Z","msg":"中國製會爆炸"},{"pid":"e21480d7c0a1fa55f856c0d4e517d0994b3469ef","tid":258263,"uid":1082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T03:12:07.000Z","msg":"我知邊款<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n果款以往都有爆開既record<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n保加利亞制造<br />\nikea pokal <br />\n<img src=\"http://www.ikea.com/PIAimages/0212627_PE366708_S5.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ikea.com%2FPIAimages%2F0212627_PE366708_S5.JPG&h=75020690&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6c6649402b2287a3610faf455fb32a1bf09c215d","tid":258263,"uid":2111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T03:14:14.000Z","msg":"真係乜撚都會發生係中國"},{"pid":"9780400eee995b123990014076d8e85e700fadef","tid":258263,"uid":2746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T03:15:22.000Z","msg":"電腦椅<br />\n橙汁<br />\n玻璃杯"},{"pid":"60c1a85f65b4a2ef839eb00146a60d2721ed130c","tid":258263,"uid":70946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T03:15:55.000Z","msg":"常溫都爆，呢下先勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}